Dataflow_FloatFieldOperationType_Multipl: Multiply the fields output values : Output = Left * Right
Dataflow_FloatFieldFalloffType_Divide: Divide the fields output values : Output = Left / Right
Dataflow_FloatFieldFalloffType_Add: Add the fields output values : Output = Left + Right
Dataflow_FloatFieldFalloffType_Substract: Subtract the fields output : Output = Left - Right
Dataflow_FloatFieldFalloffType_Min: Min of the fields output values: Output = Min(Left, Right)
Dataflow_FloatFieldFalloffType_Max: Max of the fields output values: Output = Max(Left, Right)
